OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy tonight with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fmoving northeastwards across the UK.
OL,8,FThe heaviest and most persistent rain
OL,9,Flikely over the higher ground of
OL,10,FWales. A warm and muggy night, with
OL,11,Fcoastal fog and low cloud towards the
OL,12,Fsouthwest.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FA cloudy start with some
OL,15,Frain and drizzle. Turning brighter in
OL,16,Fthe north and northwest with scattered
OL,17,Fshowers. Some warm bright spells
OL,18,Fdeveloping towards the southeast.
OL,19,FHumid in the south.
